name: Interactive CD Sampler Disc Vol. 10
overview: Interactive CD Sampler Disc Volume 10 is a Miscellaneous game, developed by Various and published by SCEA. A demo disk packaged with the PlayStation console in March 1999. It contains the following playable game demos: Contender, Crash Bandicoot 3: Warped, Spyro the Dragon, Cool Boarders 3, NHL FaceOff '99, NFL GameDay '99, Bust A Groove, Syphon Filter, Ehrgeiz, Rugrats, R4: Ridge Racer Type 4, WCW/NWO Thunder, A Bug's Life, Bust-A-Move-4 It contains the following game video: Threadz
